<p>
	The aroma of white sage is said to be herbaceous, bright, and cleansing. It&#39;s scent is thought to be powerful, without being overwhelming. White sage has a versatile aroma which pairs well with palo santo, desert sage, lemongrass, lavender, and other florals.<br />
	Enjoy the aroma and purifying effects of this white sage incense in your own home.<br />
